sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Next.js Frontend
    participant S as Spring Boot Backend
    participant Redis as Redis (rate limit counter)
    participant Docker as Docker Engine

    U->>F: Click "Run"
    F->>S: POST /execution/run (JWT + code + language)
    S->>S: Validate JWT, check RBAC (Owner/Editor only)
    S->>Redis: Check + increment per-user rate limit counter

    alt Rate limit exceeded
        S->>F: 429 Too Many Requests
        F->>U: Show rate-limit error
    else Within limit
        S->>Docker: Create ephemeral container (memory cap, CPU cap, no network)
        Docker->>Docker: Inject code + stdin
        Docker->>Docker: Execute with hard timeout

        alt Timeout exceeded
            Docker->>Docker: Force-kill container
            S->>F: Return timeout error + partial output if any
        else Completed normally
            Docker->>S: stdout, stderr, exit code
            S->>F: Return execution result
        end

        S->>Docker: Destroy container (always, regardless of outcome)
        F->>U: Display run output
    end
